# 🧑‍💼 My Resume Website

Welcome to my personal resume website, built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This project is designed to be modern, clean, and responsive – perfect for hosting with **GitHub Pages**.

🌐 **Live Site:** [https://yourusername.github.io/repo-name](https://yourusername.github.io/repo-name)  
*(Replace `yourusername` and `repo-name` with your GitHub details)*

---

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive and clean layout
- Smooth scroll navigation
- Custom sections: About, Skills, Projects, and Contact
- Built using only HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Easy to deploy with GitHub Pages

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)
- GitHub Pages for hosting

